%% E084 - Crawler state diagram - F1-8 API Admin
%% Source: docs/design/f1-8-api-admin.md (E083), architecture §3, §8
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> idle: Initial / after crawl ends

    idle --> running: POST /run (admin trigger)

    running --> success: Crawl completes OK
    running --> partial: Crawl completes with some failures
    running --> failed: Crawl aborts (error, timeout)

    success --> idle: Update CrawlerConfig
    partial --> idle: Update CrawlerConfig
    failed --> idle: Update CrawlerConfig

    note right of running
        CrawlerWorker consumes
        queue-crawler messages
    end note

    note right of failed
        Individual message failures:
        after 3 retries → DLQ
        (csjn-ruling-*-dlq)
    end note
